  "title": "🌟 BEAUTY SALES PROMOTER (ROADSHOW EXPERIENCE PREFERRED)",
  "description": "<h2>🌟 BEAUTY SALES PROMOTER (ROADSHOW EXPERIENCE PREFERRED)</h2><h3>About Us</h3><p>Apex Retail Pte Ltd is a fast-growing retail company in Singapore, committed to delivering high-quality beauty products and exceptional customer experiences. We provide a supportive, professional, and groth-oriented environment where ambitious individuals can learn, excel, and advance their careers.</p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>We are expanding our roadshow and retail sales team and are looking for dynamic Beauty Sales Promoters who:</p><ul><li><p>Engage and approach customers confidently at roadshows and retail locations</p></li><li><p>Present and recommend skincare products in a persuasive and professional manner</p></li><li><p>Close sales and achieve individual performance targets</p></li><li><p>Build strong customer relationships and deliver exceptional service</p></li></ul><h3>Salary & Benefits</h3><ul><li><p>Base Salary: $3,500 – $4,500 (based on experience)</p></li><li><p>High Commission: Up to $10,000 – $15,000 per month</p></li><li><p>CPF contributions provided</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Staff Benefits:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Birthday Leave</p></li><li><p>Medical Insurance Coverage</p></li><li><p>Leave entitlements in accordance with MOM requirements</p></li><li><p>Welcome Lunch, Team Bonding Activities, and Festive/Event Celebrations</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Singaporean / PR / LTVP only</p></li><li><p>Sales-driven, confident in approaching customers</p></li><li><p>Roadshow / beauty / direct sales experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, resilient, and target-oriented<br /></p></li></ul><p>📍 <strong>Work Locations:</strong> Orchard / Jurong</p><p>🕒 <strong>Shift Hours:</strong> 10:00am – 7:00pm | 11:30am – 8:30pm | 12:30pm – 9:30pm</p><p>📆 <strong>Work Schedule</strong>: 5 days per week with 8 off-days per month</p><p>Be part of a team that values teamwork, integrity, and efficiency.Find out more at <a href=\"https://apexretail.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://apexretail.com.sg/</a></p>",
